the right word and the right phrasing to  

739
01:00:00,640 --> 01:00:04,400
make us sound native to the language 
that our customers speak and also-

740
01:00:04,400 --> 01:00:07,920
You're talking about engineers is my sense, right?

741
01:00:07,920 --> 01:00:10,840
Yeah. Engineers is a big one, 
but even product managers, right?

742
01:00:10,840 --> 01:00:10,920
Mm-hmm.

743
01:00:10,920 --> 01:00:14,240
Like product managers know when... 
They know what the job is like. So,  

744
01:00:14,240 --> 01:00:17,600
when you come in, you say the wrong 
