01:00:17,600 --> 01:00:19,280
Don't call them project managers.

746
01:00:19,280 --> 01:00:24,920
Yeah, exactly, for example. So, I think 
that's a big part of what we have to do. So,  

747
01:00:26,520 --> 01:00:31,760
