808
01:05:12,160 --> 01:05:18,400
some burning problem that they have. So, it's your 
job when you're in the interview process to figure  

809
01:05:18,400 --> 01:05:24,920
out what that burning problem is. So, put on your 
discovery hat and go figure out what is the actual  

810
01:05:24,920 --> 01:05:31,240
job to be done of the hiring manager when they're 
bringing on a new PM onto their team? And if you  

811
01:05:31,240 --> 01:05:39,280
can do that and then make a good case that you 
