830
01:07:16,080 --> 01:07:20,080
"Oh, yeah, sure. I can tell you about the 
exact thing that I'm doing this quarter,  

831
01:07:20,080 --> 01:07:25,520
and then you'll have some level of intelligence 
about what people are actually trying to solve  

832
01:07:25,520 --> 01:07:30,080
because I think often we just get stuck in these 
very high level general types of questions like,  

833
01:07:30,080 --> 01:07:33,080
"What's the company goals sand all that kind 
of stuff, and it's like, no, you can get really  

834
01:07:33,080 --> 01:07:38,960
specific. If you were collaborating with that 
