01:13:37,840 --> 01:13:41,880
another iteration or you want to polish that 
thing and get it to be a shippable state. So,  

914
01:13:41,880 --> 01:13:48,240
you're setting up your future self to be able 
to make that decision. So, none of this is...  

915
01:13:48,240 --> 01:13:52,720
You can't go into this at the very last moment and 
say like, "Okay, now, we have to take the deadline  

916
01:13:52,720 --> 01:13:58,320
seriously." You have to do it from the beginning 
and commit to the process of going very fast,  

917
01:13:58,320 --> 01:14:04,080
iterating early, and then putting yourself in a 
position where you can say yes or no to a product.

918
01:14:04,080 --> 01:14:08,160
So interesting and so different from 
the way most companies operate. Nan,  

919
01:14:08,160 --> 01:14:10,920
this was everything I was hoping it'd be. I 
think this is going to help a lot of people  

